sourcesContent: import React, { Component } from 'react' import EditItem from './EditItem' class ItemDetail extends Component { render() { var {task, index} = this.props var isEditing = this.state.isEditing return ( {index + 1} {task.name} {task.level === 'high'? 'High' : task.level === 'low' ? 'Low' : 'Medium'} ) } } export default ItemDetail
